### [1] Owner 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "owner1@delivery-msa.com",
  "password": "owner1111",
  "name": "사장님",
  "phone": "010-2222-2222",
  "role": "OWNER"
}

### [2] Owner 로그인
# accessToken, refreshToken 복사해서 아래 변수에 붙여넣기
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "owner1@delivery-msa.com",
  "password": "owner1111"
}

### [3] 가게 등록
# X-User-Id: 위 응답의 accessToken을 Authorization에 사용 (Gateway가 X-User-Id 주입)
# category: KOREAN, CHINESE, JAPANESE, PIZZA, BURGER, CHICKEN, CAFE, OTHER
POST http://localhost:8080/api/owner/restaurants
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <OWNER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "name": "테스트 치킨집",
  "phone": "02-1234-5678",
  "address": "서울시 강남구 테헤란로 1",
  "category": "CHICKEN",
  "minOrderAmount": 15000,
  "deliveryFee": 3000,
  "estimatedDeliveryMinutes": 30
}

### [4] 메뉴 등록 (restaurantId는 [3] 응답에서 복사)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/owner/restaurants/<RESTAURANT_ID>/menus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <OWNER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "name": "후라이드 치킨",
  "description": "바삭한 후라이드",
  "price": 18000,
  "categoryName": "치킨",
  "sortOrder": 1,
  "options": [
    {
      "name": "사이즈",
      "items": [
        { "name": "보통", "extraPrice": 0 },
        { "name": "대", "extraPrice": 3000 }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### [5] 메뉴 추가 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/api/owner/restaurants/<RESTAURANT_ID>/menus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <OWNER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "name": "양념 치킨",
  "description": "달콤한 양념",
  "price": 19000,
  "categoryName": "치킨",
  "sortOrder": 2
}

### [6] 가게 오픈
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/owner/restaurants/<RESTAURANT_ID>/open
Authorization: Bearer <OWNER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### [7] 내 가게 주문 목록 조회 (주문 들어온 후 확인용)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/owner/orders?restaurantId=<RESTAURANT_ID>
Authorization: Bearer <OWNER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### [8] 주문 수락 (orderId는 customer.http [3] 응답에서 복사)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/owner/orders/<ORDER_ID>/accept
Authorization: Bearer <OWNER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### [9] 픽업 준비 완료
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/owner/orders/<ORDER_ID>/ready
Authorization: Bearer <OWNER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### [10] 가게 마감
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/owner/restaurants/<RESTAURANT_ID>/close
Authorization: Bearer <OWNER_ACCESS_TOKEN>
